channel.title: Hey guys, I need some help :(
channel.description:
Alrighty when i try to login to moparscape using the webclient version I first go to the server status page, and click on the first server I see(usually the top one), now all of a sudden when I click the server i want to play it comes up with a new webclient window...now when this happens sometimes it loads(and freezes), and the other times is comes up with this:
Sorry, an error has occured whilst loading RuneScape
To fix this try the following (inorder):
1)Try closing ALL open web-browser windows, and reloading 2)Try clearing your web-browser cache from tools --> internet options 3)Try using a different game world 4)Try rebooting your computer 5)Try selecting a different version of Java from the play-game menu
And I have no idea how to do # 2, and 5 So if anyone could please tell me how to fix this error it would be very much appreciated :(
oh and this is the stuff in the little black box, underneath the web client:
[07:42:51] Starting MoparScape 3.2 [07:42:52] [07:42:52] News: Welcome to MoparScape 3.2, the pinnacle of RS2 [07:42:52] News: first generation client editing, with a built [07:42:52] News: in private server, music player capable of playing [07:42:52] News: both midis and mp3s, item/object/npc changer/viewer and [07:42:52] News: much much more. For updates, suggestions, or help [07:42:52] News: please visit the forums at www.moparisthebest.com/smf [07:42:52] News: and post in my thread. Y'all have fun. [07:42:52] News: [07:42:52] News: For online servers, look at the [07:42:52] News: server status list at moparisthebest.com [07:42:52] News: [07:42:52] News: -moparisthebest [07:42:52] Server : wackoscape.no-ip.org:43594 Error: loaderror bobConnecting to fileserver 10
so any one that could help, please do it is very, very, very appreciated :(
